rComments: Prof. Lee is very friendly and helpful. He always makes sure that all the students understand the material given after class. What he explains in the class are very useful for the exam, so take notes. His slides are very informative too.

Professor Lee is a very friendly and knowledgeable teacher. He may be unclear at times, but he is extremely approachable. With that being said, Professor Lee is open to helping students out. You should have a basic knowledge of statistics for the course.  All in all, this class isn't that bad if you come to lecture and pay attention.
